main_body:
Directive 2004/17/EC shall not apply to contracts awarded by contracting entities and intended to enable them to carry out the following parcel and courier services in Denmark:
(a) Domestic Business to Business (BtB) parcel services;
(b) International Business to Business (BtB) parcel services;
(c) Domestic light goods/pallet goods services;
(d) International light goods/pallet goods services;
(e) Domestic courier and express services; and
(f) International courier and express services.
